content:
Create an Intent from an Einstein Conversation Mining Report

You can add excerpts to an intent thatâ€™s part of an intent set directly from Einstein Conversation Mining. Then, share the intents across many bots.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience with the Service Intelligence add-on. Setup for Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Select a report and click the summary name of a topic.
Select some excerpts, and then click New Intent.
Select whether to create an intent set or add to an intent set. Then, select or add your intent set, and include details about your new intent.
Save your changes.
title: Creating Intent in Service Cloud
